    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《动物多米诺》是一款棋盘式 roguelike 卡牌构建游戏，玩家需要探索强力组合冲击高分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282420/extras/9180a1b86b11b1b4619e9fc6631a0bd1.poster.avif?t=1771465142\" width=780 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282420/extras/9180a1b86b11b1b4619e9fc6631a0bd1.webm?t=1771465142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282420/extras/9180a1b86b11b1b4619e9fc6631a0bd1.mp4?t=1771465142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >巧妙搭配</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过喂食和获取纪念品的方式升级动物牌，把初始卡组变成大师杰作。巧妙利用棋盘元素，进一步提升得分。专注于不同种类和颜色的动物，利用各种强化永久提升卡牌能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282420/extras/0ce23619232723e87afb7121c4582381.poster.avif?t=1771465142\" width=780 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282420/extras/0ce23619232723e87afb7121c4582381.webm?t=1771465142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282420/extras/0ce23619232723e87afb7121c4582381.mp4?t=1771465142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收集控狂喜</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从可爱小动物到神话生物，你能在游戏中看见各种动物。你可以从众多动物管理员中选择一名陪你开始游戏，礼品店还有大量的食物和纪念品供客官挑选。找到超稀有的神话动物，解锁并收集所有物品吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 位动物管理员</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >27 种食物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >159 种动物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 种纪念品</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282420/extras/c552234e05c20d039a9c2b0a8ed8672e.poster.avif?t=1771465142\" width=780 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282420/extras/c552234e05c20d039a9c2b0a8ed8672e.webm?t=1771465142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282420/extras/c552234e05c20d039a9c2b0a8ed8672e.mp4?t=1771465142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无尽模式：完成一个月的挑战后可选择开启无尽模式，不断冲击更高分吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特殊事件：每周末会带来额外挑战的特别活动，有时甚至会改变棋盘布局！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >种子开局：尝试在相同的随机事件下打破朋友的记录，找到完美组合再破新高吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高难度挑战：挑战自己，打通 8 种难度吧——包括但不限于：更高的目标分数要求、蚂蚁会入侵你的卡组，等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282420/extras/5e0c330f85fccb0fded1b850380b2243.poster.avif?t=1771465142\" width=780 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282420/extras/5e0c330f85fccb0fded1b850380b2243.webm?t=1771465142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282420/extras/5e0c330f85fccb0fded1b850380b2243.mp4?t=1771465142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
